sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant D as Daemon
    participant R as AgentRuntime

    C->>D: POST /v1/interactive/turn
    D->>R: enqueue
    D-->>C: stream_url
    C->>D: GET stream SSE

    loop events
        R-->>D: stream event
        D-->>C: InteractiveTurnStreamEvent
    end

    C->>D: POST /v1/sessions/id/active-turn
    D->>R: cancel
    D-->>C: cancelled
